snippet.title: MANNEQUIN MACHINE trailer new horror game
snippet.description:
"Mannequin machine" is a first-person psychological horror game with camera effects that tells the story of working in a mannequin factory. Beware of the evil at the heart of the plant, it drives its victims crazy.
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3101180/Mannequin_machine/
